name: Dear Christie Farewell Show Ticket 7/28/2012
description:
Order your ticket online to guarantee your spot in the crowd! This is a show no one wants to miss, so snag your ticket before someone else does!

Opening Artists: WC Lindsay, Set Audio, The Said and Done, Liberty Deep Down

Doors: 5:30PM

Also in support is is Cole Stillz organization "Everyone's Beautiful".  Come out, enjoy the night and support some awesome causes!

IF YOUR TICKETS ARE ORDERED AFTER 5PM ON 7/23/2012 THEY WILL BE CONSIDERED "WILL CALL" AND WILL BE WAITING AT THE DOOR FOR YOU.
